OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FRetatrutide is one of the latest
OL,7,Fweight loss drugs. It's in Phase 3
OL,8,Fclinical trials, and not yet licensed
OL,9,Ffor personal use anywhere in the world
OL,10,Funless you are part of a trial.
OL,12,FIt's made by one of the biggest drug
OL,13,Fmakers, Eli Lilly, the same company
OL,14,Fthat manufacture Mounjaro.
OL,16,FThere was a significant price increase
OL,17,Fin Mounjaro last September by 170%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
