OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FEli Lilly previously stated this
OL,7,Fadjustment was to bring UK prices into
OL,8,Falignment with European and other
OL,9,Fdeveloped countries to ensure fair
OL,10,Fglobal contributions to medical
OL,11,Finnovation, as the drug was initially
OL,12,Flaunched below the European average.
OL,14,FSome say that the high cost of weight
OL,15,Floss drugs is what drives them to the
OL,16,Fgrey market.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
