OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FIt is currently illegal to advertise
OL,7,Fand sell Retatrutide for personal use.
OL,8,FOur reporter, Chloe Seaton, went
OL,9,Fundercover to understand how these
OL,10,Fsellers operate.
OL,12,FOne beauty clinic in Wales advertised
OL,13,FRetatrutide for weight-loss on their
OL,14,Fsocial media account. Our reporter was
OL,15,Fable to book a 15 minute "Free
OL,16,FRetatrutide Consultation" through
OL,17,Ftheir online booking platform.
OL,19,FThe seller said Retatrutide is more
OL,20,Feconomical, being cheaper than
OL,21,FMounjaro and Wegovy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
