PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FThey said: "It's a bigger pen so
OL,7,Fyou've got 40 mill in there, so if you
OL,8,Fwere to stick it on the 2.5 which is
OL,9,Fthe lowest dose you can have."
OL,11,FThe seller disclosed they were aware
OL,12,FRetatrutide was "not FDA approved".
OL,14,FThe Food and Drug Administration (FDA)
OL,15,Fis responsible for regulating
OL,16,Fprescription and over-the-counter
OL,17,Fpharmaceuticals within the United
OL,18,FStates.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
