PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FIn comparison, the Medicines and
OL,7,FHealthcare products Regulatory Agency
OL,8,F(MHRA) regulate medicines, medical
OL,9,Fdevices, and blood components for
OL,10,Ftransfusion in the UK.
OL,12,F"So, I got it through my pharmacy
OL,13,Fright, it's not FDA approved so I have
OL,14,Fto tell you that", they said.
OL,16,F"Whereas Mounjaro, Wegovy, all those
OL,17,Fare, this isn't right, which most
OL,18,Fproducts are not, there are so many on
OL,19,Fthe market that are not FDA approved
OL,20,Fbut we use."
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@QO]xD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
