PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FWhen asked if there were any side
OL,7,Feffects to Retatrutide, the supplier
OL,8,Fsaid they were aware of side effects
OL,9,Fassociated with Mounjaro and Wegovy,
OL,10,Flike nausea.
OL,12,FBut, when it came to Retatrutide, the
OL,13,Fonly side effect they had heard of was
OL,14,F"sulfur burps."
OL,16,FWhen it comes to the price, the
OL,17,Fsupplier was charging #175 for one pen
OL,18,Fcontaining 40 milligrams of
OL,19,FRetatrutide.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
