OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FResponding to our investigation, the
OL,7,Fclinic did not deny that they supply
OL,8,For advertise Retatrutide.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the clinic
OL,11,Fcharacterised the meeting as "an
OL,12,Finformal discussion," adding:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
