SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,F"At no point during this meeting was a
OL,7,Fclinical consultation undertaken, a
OL,8,Fprescription issued, or any medication
OL,9,Fsupplied. The individual did not
OL,10,Fproceed with an assessment and
OL,11,Ftherefore no medical questionnaire,
OL,12,Fweight, height, BMI assessment,
OL,13,Fmedical history review, or prescribing
OL,14,Fdecision was completed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,F"Had the individual wished to proceed
OL,7,Ffurther, my normal process would have
OL,8,Fbeen to obtain the relevant medical
OL,9,Finformation and screening
OL,10,Fdocumentation before referring the
OL,11,Fcase to an appropriately qualified
OL,12,Fprescriber.
OL,14,F"Any decision regarding suitability
OL,15,Fwould be made by the prescriber
OL,16,Ffollowing review of the completed
OL,17,Fconsultation information. No such
OL,18,Fprocess was commenced because the
OL,19,Findividual advised that she wished to
OL,20,Fconsider her options and discuss the
OL,21,Fmatter with her partner first.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,F"The comments regarding side effects
OL,7,Fwere made in the context of a general
OL,8,Fconversation about experiences
OL,9,Freported by individuals who have used
OL,10,Fsimilar products. They were not
OL,11,Fprovided as part of a clinical
OL,12,Fconsultation, prescribing decision, or
OL,13,Fmedical assessment.
OL,15,F"I am an aesthetics practitioner and
OL,16,Fdo not make prescribing decisions.
OL,17,FWhere appropriate, clients who wish to
OL,18,Fproceed are required to complete the
OL,19,Frelevant consultation process and any
OL,20,Fprescribing decisions are made by a
OL,21,Fqualified prescriber."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FIt's not yet possible to get the drug
OL,7,Fprescribed legitimately, so despite
OL,8,Fwhat sellers of the drug may say,
OL,9,Fthere is not guarantee what is in the
OL,10,Fvial.
OL,12,FBut that's not stopped people willing
OL,13,Fto take the risks, in the hopes of
OL,14,Flosing weight.
OL,16,FOne woman told ITV News that due to
OL,17,Fthe Mounjaro price hike in January she
OL,18,Fstarted to look for alternative
OL,19,Fsuppliers on the grey market in China.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FShe said, "So I started looking into
OL,7,FReta, through the grey market in
OL,8,FChina, and spent a lot of time
OL,9,Fresearching that and ended up going
OL,10,Fthrough that sort of means instead.
OL,12,F"I was very worried about making sure
OL,13,Fthat it was going to be you know a
OL,14,Ftrusted source and that what was in
OL,15,Fthe vial was what it said.
OL,17,F"I had some nausea at the start, that
OL,18,Fwas quite worrying at the time because
OL,19,Fit stops you wanting to eat anything,
OL,20,Fso started having protein shakes just
OL,21,Fso that I could have enough protein."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FEli Lilly have previously said that
OL,7,Fanyone selling the product outside of
OL,8,Fclinical trials are operating
OL,9,Fillegally and that such products pose
OL,10,Fa safety risk.
OL,12,FReacting to ITV's undercover footage,
OL,13,FDr Sue Kenneally, a specialist obesity
OL,14,Fmedicine physician, said she is "very
OL,15,Fworried."
OL,17,FShe said, "I'd love to know where her
OL,18,F(the seller) pharmacy is, because I am
OL,19,Fnot aware of any regulated pharmacy
OL,20,Fwho will ever to give that to someone
OL,21,Ffor personal use.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,F"For her to not check your medical
OL,7,Fhistory at all, in one way, she can
OL,8,Fdefend that and say, well, I've got no
OL,9,Fguidance about this, so I'll just make
OL,10,Fmy own rules. But on the other hand,
OL,11,Fit's extremely dangerous.
OL,13,F"So, to have not even ask you whether
OL,14,Fyou have a history of pancreatitis or
OL,15,Fthyroid cancer, at the very least, I
OL,16,Fthink is really indefensible."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
