PN,43915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782224342
OL,3,CHow 'grey market' sellers are cashing
OL,4,Cin on an illicit weight loss drug
OL,6,FThe MHRA is the UK's medicines
OL,7,Fregulator and has issued strict
OL,8,Fwarning about purchasing medications
OL,9,Ffrom the grey market stating such
OL,10,Fproducts are "potentially deadly."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/15
